{"tid":1560961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以色列總理內塔尼亞胡揚言連任後吞併西岸土地  阿拉伯國家譴責以色列侵略及違反國際法破壞和平","createTime":"2019-09-11T11:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T05:12:21.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8e35b6147d0e654d4df9380ca6a972fb738d31","tid":1560961,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190911/s00005/1568191289443/%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E5%90%9E%E4%BD%B5%E8%A5%BF%E5%B2%B8%E5%A4%A7%E7%89%87%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80-%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%E6%96%A5%E6%AF%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E9%80%B2%E7%A8%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00005%2F1568191289443%2F%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%2590%259E%25E4%25BD%25B5%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258D%2580-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E6%258B%2589%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%25AF%2581%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E9%2580%25B2%25E7%25A8%258B&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=f4efdb9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00005%2F1568191289443%2F%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%2590%259E%25E4%25BD%25B5%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258D%2580-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E6%258B%2589%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%25AF%2581%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E9%2580%25B2%25E7%25A8%258B&h=1a5ecfa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190911/s00005/1568191289443/%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E5%90%9E%E4%BD%B5%E8%A5%BF%E5%B2%B8%E5%A4%A7%E7%89%87%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80-%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%E6%96%A5%E6%AF%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E9%80%B2%E7%A8%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n以色列下周二（17日）舉行大選，總理內塔尼亞胡昨（10日）表示，若他在大選中連任，將會吞併約旦河西岸佔領區的約旦河谷（Jordan Valley）及死海北部，隨即惹來阿拉伯國家譴責，斥此舉是違反國際法的「危險發展和以色列新的侵略」，巴勒斯坦官員亦炮轟內塔尼亞胡「毁掉所有達成和平的機會」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內塔尼亞胡周二發表電視演說，身旁的架子擺着一張約旦河谷地圖，他說：「選舉後，以色列的主權可以立即延伸到一個地方。若我獲得各以色列民眾在採取這項行動上的明確授權&hellip;&hellip;今日我宣布我打算將以色列下屆政府組成後的主權延伸到約旦河谷和死海北部。」目前民調顯示，內塔尼亞胡領導的庫德集團與反對派的藍白聯盟支持度咬緊，內塔尼亞胡的競爭對手指控他在選前一周耍花招，旨在爭取右翼民族主義者選票。<br />\n<br />\n巴勒斯坦高級官員阿什拉維（Hanan Ashrawi）表示，內塔尼亞胡「不只摧毁兩國方案，還摧毁所有達成和平的機會」。阿拉伯聯盟亦發聲明譴責內塔尼亞胡的吞併計劃，指摘這是危險的發展和侵略，「破壞和平進程任何進展的機會並摧毁所有基礎」。<br />\n<br />\n約旦河谷約佔約旦河西岸地區面積的三分之一，以色列右翼政客一直將這個具戰略地區視為他們絕不撤離的領土一部分，視之為以色列東部邊界。以色列在1967年第三次中東戰爭期間佔領約旦河西岸，隨後開始在此地興建猶太殖民區。<br />\n<br />\n（BBC/法新社）"},{"pid":"95e3272c320848e500147b746ebf7a80120ddfb2","tid":1560961,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"38fc807e6f8f32842d33ba621a02cf0b387f1059","tid":1560961,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"Support Israel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"